{"tid":1716194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到隔離post講起許廷鏗，我諗起佢首面具","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:18:44.000Z","uid":116214,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee08bab73229be3cc89928183bef9e6a5340fa5b","tid":1716194,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"發過要發的夢 但熱烈漸覺冰凍<br />\n<br />\n跌過痛過便會懂<br />\n<br />\n誰在作弄 沉默背後也想發狂<br />\n<br />\n很想找一剎來放縱 斗膽一次如反恐<br />\n<br />\n也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝<br />\n<br />\n衝出困局 形象似義勇軍般英勇<br />\n<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通<br />\n<br />\n如戴著面具去掩飾倦容<br />\n<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<br />\n<br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌詞都幾有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ee649cbdad4147a0b71a85341eece3851d2ed8","tid":1716194,"uid":332860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"義勇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d8109063728342a01f383d4b3c91b0c9b9b0a8","tid":1716194,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ee649cbdad4147a0b71a85341eece3851d2ed8","tid":1716194,"uid":332860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"義勇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"勇武軍囉"},{"pid":"f0e668441cc1bd18c973588a3434b75bfec52142","tid":1716194,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ee649cbdad4147a0b71a85341eece3851d2ed8","tid":1716194,"uid":332860